        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a large bowl – this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong> to the dressing and gently mix together – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
